You're better off not knowing him.

00:49:34.680 --> 00:49:36.179
Why? You two didn't get along?

00:49:36.180 --> 00:49:37.280
And we never will.

00:49:40.250 --> 00:49:41.549
I'm going to go on in.

00:49:41.550 --> 00:49:43.350
- Okay. - Okay.

00:49:45.250 --> 00:49:46.620
Oh, here, let me get that.

00:49:47.020 --> 00:49:48.490
- I'll take it in. - Thanks.

00:49:50.090 --> 00:49:52.129
- Hey, Sung Je Yeon. - Yes?

00:49:52.130 --> 00:49:55.459
You've known Kim Seok Joo way longer than me, so how could you not know?

00:49:55.460 --> 00:49:57.900
Just because we go way back, doesn't mean we're close.

00:49:58.370 --> 00:50:00.839
For you and Kim Seok Joo to be brothers,

00:50:00.840 --> 00:50:02.200
our CEO...

00:50:02.870 --> 00:50:04.110
and your father...

00:50:04.310 --> 00:50:05.310
What?

00:50:05.870 --> 00:50:08.140
She's your CEO?

00:50:08.710 --> 00:50:11.180
That's quite a reaction.

00:50:15.480 --> 00:50:16.990
I don't have anything against her.

00:50:17.550 --> 00:50:19.020
Though I can't say the same for her.

