So, let me get this straight.

00:57:49.170 --> 00:57:51.970
Do you want it to rip eventually? Or...

00:57:52.510 --> 00:57:54.280
do you want something that takes a lot of effort...

00:57:54.780 --> 00:57:56.579
to rip? What's the end goal here?

